On this artist journey it is imperative that your team is professional, timely, passionate, kind and will aid/assist in getting you to your “THERE!” @creativeclassicagency has been the team that I didn’t know that I needed! I just returned from Houston and Camp CCA where we were charged up with prayer, had an entertainment attorney speak to us about contracts, a branding rep, Grammy and Stellar Awards reps as well as a label rep. We ended the week with dinner and a pool party. Having a management company ( especially Gospel) that INVESTS in their artists is RARE in 2023! Thank you and happy birthaversary @nicoleheyward @jiles.king @shekinahmitchell @_mayorchris_  #camp #seeker #maricachisolm
